Heather Lauren Olson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heather_Lauren_Olson 0 Heather Lauren Olson (born November 12, 1982 in San Jose, California) is an American actress. Olson is probably best known for her recurring role as Jan Spears in the NBC-TV daytime soap opera series Days of Our Lives (2000-2004).
